        			<div class="thumbnail-wrap">

        	<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://example2.com/how-do-software-providers-stay-afloat-in-2022-16/">How Do Software Providers Stay Afloat in 2022</a></h2>
        	
        	<div class="entry-meta">
        
        			<span class="entry-author"><a href="https://example2.com/author/r9ges/" title="Posts by r9ges" rel="author">r9ges</a></span>
        	
        			<span class="sep author-sep">&middot;</span>	
        	
        			<span class="entry-date">July 1, 2023</span>
        	
        	
        	
        
        </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
